parse.title: List of towns and cities with 100,000 or more inhabitants/country: L-M-N-O

text.*:
This is a list of towns and cities in the world in alphabetical order beginning with letters L, M, N and O, by country believed to have 100,000 or more inhabitants. Unless otherwise noted, populations are based on 2006 United Nations estimates.
